This is how to sort_numbers of numbers:
   When isstring of numbers, then:
      The answer is numbers
   End when
   Remember that n is numbers's length
   Remember that i is 0
   Do this n times:
      Remember that j is 0
      Do this diff of n and 1 times:
         Remember that a is item j in numbers
         Remember that b is item (sum of j and 1) in numbers
         When a is more than b, then:
            Remember that item j in numbers is b
            Remember that item (sum of j and 1) in numbers is a
         End when
         Increase j
      End do
      Increase i
   End do
   The answer is numbers
